<promed@promedmail.org>

[Polio vaccination activities are on the list of activities suffering collateral damage as a result of the COVID-19 pandemic. In the early stages of the pandemic, vaccination activities were interrupted, now there is fear on the part of the population that visiting health facilities for vaccination will put them at high risk of transmission of the SARS-CoV-2. A very sad outcome of the pandemic. - Mod.MPP]
